statements: SELECT * FROM LeadScoring WHERE lead_id = 1;
SELECT user_id, total_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE website_interaction_score > 50;
SELECT lead_id, form_submission_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE total_score < 100;
SELECT * FROM LeadScoring WHERE website_interaction_score = 20 AND form_submission_score = 30;
SELECT lead_id, user_id, total_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE user_id = 5;
SELECT * FROM LeadScoring WHERE total_score > 100 ORDER BY user_id DESC;
SELECT user_id, website_interaction_score, form_submission_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE form_submission_score > 50;
SELECT lead_id, total_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE user_id = 101 AND website_interaction_score < 20;
SELECT lead_id, user_id, total_score FROM LeadScoring WHERE form_submission_score = 0 ORDER BY total_score DESC, user_id ASC;
SELECT MAX(total_score) AS highest_score, AVG(total_score) AS average_score FROM LeadScoring;
SELECT * FROM Lead_Interactions WHERE lead_id = 1;
SELECT form_name, submission_time FROM Form_Submissions WHERE form_id = 10;
SELECT page_visited, interaction_time FROM Lead_Interactions ORDER BY interaction_time DESC;
SELECT event_type, interaction_time FROM Lead_Interactions WHERE page_visited LIKE '%contact%';
SELECT lead_id, page_visited FROM Lead_Interactions WHERE interaction_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Lead_Interactions WHERE event_type = 'click' ORDER BY interaction_time DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT page_visited, COUNT(*) as visit_count FROM Lead_Interactions GROUP BY page_visited ORDER BY visit_count DESC;
SELECT lead_id, MAX(interaction_time) as last_interaction FROM Lead_Interactions GROUP BY lead_id;

SELECT lead_id, form_name, submission_time FROM Lead_Interactions INNER JOIN Form_Submissions ON Lead_Interactions.lead_id = Form_Submissions.lead_id WHERE Form_Submissions.submission_time > '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM Form_Submissions WHERE submission_data->'$.completed' = 'true';
SELECT * FROM leads;
SELECT lead_id, lead_name FROM leads ORDER BY lead_name ASC;
SELECT lead_id, lead_email FROM leads WHERE lead_interaction_count > 5;
SELECT * FROM interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'Demo';
SELECT lead_id, form_name FROM form_submissions ORDER BY submission_timestamp DESC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM leads;
SELECT * FROM interactions WHERE interaction_type = 'Email' ORDER BY interaction_timestamp DESC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_interaction_count FROM leads WHERE lead_interaction_count > 5;
SELECT lead_name, form_name FROM leads JOIN form_submissions ON leads.lead_id = form_submissions.lead_id;
SELECT lead_name, COUNT(*) AS total_interactions FROM leads JOIN interactions ON leads.lead_id = interactions.lead_id GROUP BY lead_name ORDER BY total_interactions DESC;
SELECT * FROM Lead_Interactions;
SELECT user_id, interaction_type FROM Lead_Interactions ORDER BY timestamp DESC;

SELECT form_id, COUNT(*) AS submissions_count FROM Form_Submissions WHERE timestamp BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31' GROUP BY form_id ORDER BY submissions_count DESC;
SELECT user_id, MAX(timestamp) AS last_visit FROM Website_Visits GROUP BY user_id;

SELECT * FROM Lead_Interactions JOIN Form_Submissions ON Lead_Interactions.user_id = Form_Submissions.user_id WHERE Lead_Interactions.timestamp > '2022-01-01' ORDER BY Form_Submissions.timestamp ASC LIMIT 5;
